comments: VanVleet (TOR) brings his hand toward Conley's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the drive.
Conley (UTA) brings his off-arm toward VanVleet's (TOR) side and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Clarkson (UTA) places his hand momentarily on Siakam's (TOR) side and the contact is marginal.
Achiuwa (TOR) is already in Clarkson's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Kessler (UTA) and Achiuwa (TOR) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs off ball.
VanVleet (TOR) is turning away from Clarkson (UTA) as marginal contact occurs after the release.
Markkanen (UTA) steps slightly towards Barnes (TOR) and marginal contact occurs prior to Barnes' upward shooting motion.
Markkanen (UTA) brings his arm down and makes contact with Barnes' (TOR) arm as he defends the shot.
Achiuwa (TOR) makes clean contact with the ball prior to any ensuing contact with Kessler's (UTA) arm, which is deemed marginal.
Clarkson (UTA) is moving alongside VanVleet's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs as VanVleet passes the ball.
Kessler (UTA) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Boucher (TOR) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Agbaji (UTA) and Achiuwa (TOR) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Achiuwa (TOR) extends his forearm into Clarkson's (UTA) body and the contact affects his SQBR during the drive.
Achiuwa (TOR) establishes himself in Conley's (UTA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Kessler (UTA) makes contact with Trent Jr.'s (TOR) hand while the ball is on Trent Jr.'s finger tips, and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Trent Jr. (TOR) and Clarkson (UTA) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Barnes (TOR) wraps Markkanen (UTA) as he receives the pass.
